Package net.pl3x.map.api

Class JsonArrayWrapper

java.lang.Object
net.pl3x.map.api.JsonArrayWrapper
public class JsonArrayWrapper extends Object
Represents a wrapped JsonArray with extra 'add' methods, because Google made it a final class.
